Zhang Ziyi ranked among "50 most beautiful female celebrities"
2013-03-19 06:16:17 GMT
Famous Chinese actress Zhang Ziyi ranks 23 (1st among those of Chinese descent) in the "50 most beautiful female celebrities" chosen by Los Angeles Times on March 17.Following is the original description by the paper:Number 23: Zhang ZiyiWhere you've seen her: On the big screenWhy we love her: She kicked butt in "Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon," enchanted in "Memoirs of a Geisha," showed off her tap-dancing skills (no, really!) in "Princess Raccoon," and was the youngest person ever to sit on the jury of the Cannes Film Festival. Plus, she survived "Rush Hour 2" with her dignity intact!(Agencies)
